# AI Aliens - Weekly Content Schedule

## Overview

Each location runs for **1 week** (Sunday to Friday), with Saturday off. New location starts every Sunday.

**Annual capacity:** 52 locations/year

---

## Weekly Schedule

| Day | Content | Time | Platforms | Character |
|-----|---------|------|-----------|-----------|
| **Sun** | Intro Video | 8pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | Gorb solo |
| **Mon** | Photos 1-5 | 5pm | Instagram (carousel + stories), TikTok, YouTube (slideshow) | Both |
| **Tue** | Gorb's Story | 5pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | Gorb solo |
| **Wed** | Photos 6-10 | 5pm | Instagram (carousel + stories), TikTok, YouTube (slideshow) | Both |
| **Thu** | Pleck's Story | 5pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | Pleck solo |
| **Fri** | Review Video | 5pm | Instagram, TikTok, YouTube | Gorb or Pleck solo |
| **Sat** | — | — | — | — |

---

## Content Per Location

| Content Type | Count | Notes |
|--------------|-------|-------|
| Intro Video | 1 | Landing zone spot, Gorb solo |
| Photo Carousels | 2 | 5 photos each (4 generic + 1 food per carousel), both characters |
| Gorb Story | 1 | Generic spot, Gorb solo — enthusiastic anecdote |
| Pleck Story | 1 | Generic spot, Pleck solo — grumpy complaint |
| Review Video | 1 | Generic spot, solo speaker based on Review_Speaker field |

---

## Video Content Structure

All videos are **single-clip, single-character monologues** (8 seconds, ~5-6 seconds of dialogue).

| Video Type | Speaker | Tone |
|------------|---------|------|
| Intro | Gorb | Excited, enthusiastic arrival |
| Gorb Story | Gorb | Enthusiastic anecdote about location |
| Pleck Story | Pleck | Grumpy complaint about Gorb or location |
| Review | Gorb OR Pleck | Glowing (Gorb) or critical (Pleck) based on Review_Speaker |

---

## Spots Required Per Location

| Spot Type | Count | Used By |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| landing_zone | 1 | Intro |
| food_vendor | 2 | Snapshots (1 Mon, 1 Wed) |
| generic | 12 | Stories (2) + Snapshots (8) + Review (1) + buffer |

**Total: 15 spots per location**

---

## Other Requirements Per Location

| Tab | Count | Notes |
|-----|-------|-------|
| Foods | 2 | 1 per snapshot day |
| Dialogue | 1 row | Intro_Line, Gorb_Story, Pleck_Story, Review_Line, Review_Speaker |

---

## Global Pools (Shared Across Locations)

| Pool | Current Count | Weekly Usage | Runway |
|------|---------------|--------------|--------|
| Photo Activities (intro) | ~3 | 1 | Reusable |
| Photo Activities (gorb_story) | ~3 | 1 | Reusable |
| Photo Activities (pleck_story) | ~3 | 1 | Reusable |
| Photo Activities (review) | ~2 | 1 | Reusable |
| Photo Activities (general) | ~20 | 8 | Reusable |
| Photo Activities (food) | ~5 | 2 | Reusable |
| Time of Day | 5 | Varies | Reusable |

**Note:** Jokes tab is no longer used.

---

## Weekly Platform Totals

| Platform | Posts/Week | Recommended Range |
|----------|------------|-------------------|
| Instagram Feed | 6 | 3-7 ✓ |
| Instagram Stories | 6 days | Daily ✓ |
| TikTok | 6 videos | 2-5 (slightly over) ✓ |
| YouTube | 6 videos | 2-5 (slightly over) ✓ |

